            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D795776" rel="nofollow">風見暉一</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2158026" rel="nofollow">Autumn_Dream</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2070349" rel="nofollow">朱丶工作室</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2305577" rel="nofollow">Xr白糖</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2201192" rel="nofollow">最亮的派大星</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 2 月 17 日消息，realme 今日官宣将推一款<span class="hot-topic">真我 Neo7</span>X 手机，该机定位“<strong>千元价位段战略新品</strong>”，现已开启 1 元预约。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1458" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/2/773b7ae7-c1e4-4012-a522-e378b98caf83.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="realme 真我 Neo7X 千元机新品官宣，入网证件照公布" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: justify;">电商平台显示，该机型号为&nbsp;<strong>RMX5071</strong>，新机已经入网，IT之家附证件照如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="791" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/2/d7e472f7-8712-4059-974f-2c89059621a0.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="realme 真我 Neo7X 千元机新品官宣，入网证件照公布" width="590" /></p><p style="text-align: justify;">入网信息显示，该机支持 5G 网络，配有屏下指纹，<strong>搭载&nbsp;6.67 英寸&nbsp;2400×1080 分辨率 OLED 屏</strong>；配有&nbsp;5860mAh 电池，以及&nbsp;2.3GHz 8 核 CPU。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="794" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/2/b1f76ee0-9c75-43e4-b3d3-b9101a6c2bd3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="realme 真我 Neo7X 千元机新品官宣，入网证件照公布" width="591" /></p><p style="text-align: justify;">新机重量&nbsp;194g，厚度&nbsp;7.97mm，可选&nbsp;6GB / 8GB / 12GB / 16GB 内存和&nbsp;128GB / 256GB / 512GB / 1TB 存储，<strong>后置 50MP + 2MP 双摄、前置 16MP 镜头</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="786" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/2/f5071138-de57-457c-8e56-2e12ef990465.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="realme 真我 Neo7X 千元机新品官宣，入网证件照公布" width="593" /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
